Nicholas and I visited my parents tonight and came home around 10:30pm.&nbsp; After checking his grades and freaking out we proceeded to have pillow talk with slight hopes of sleeping.&nbsp; It is currently 1:50AM and we are alertly reading and watching Sports Night.&nbsp; *sigh*&nbsp; The presents are taunting me.&nbsp; 

